<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="61700000t" end="70500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">可恶</p>
<p begin="181400000t" end="201500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">艾连 你醒了吗</p>
<p begin="201500000t" end="231100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">再忍耐一下哦 没事的</p>
<p begin="238200000t" end="257800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">你也没事吗 希丝特莉亚</p>
<p begin="261500000t" end="280700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">艾连 你听我说</p>
<p begin="286500000t" end="314100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">我的父亲不论以前还是接下来</p>
<p begin="314500000t" end="345300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">都会是被留在墙里的所有人类的同伴</p>
<p begin="345800000t" end="367900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">我们之间有很深的误会</p>
<p begin="375000000t" end="408300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">他们的确处处妨碍调查军团</p>
<p begin="408700000t" end="432100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">也杀了尼克神父灭口</p>
<p begin="436700000t" end="462100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">但是父亲只能这么做</p>
<p begin="465000000t" end="497600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">这全都是为了人类着想而不得不做的事</p>
<p begin="502200000t" end="543000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">希丝特莉亚 接着由我来说明吧</p>
<p begin="589300000t" end="618100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">我想起来了 好像…</p>
<p begin="622700000t" end="659800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">我最后记得的就是看到这两个人</p>
<p begin="665700000t" end="683600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">到底过了多久了</p>
<p begin="687400000t" end="708600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">兵长 阿尔敏…</p>
<p begin="708600000t" end="731100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">调查军团现在怎么样了</p>
<p begin="797500000t" end="822500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">这个墙壁怎么回事</p>
<p begin="827500000t" end="843300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">还发着淡淡的光</p>
<p begin="849600000t" end="872500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">完全搞不清楚时间</p>
<p begin="878400000t" end="903400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">不 不对</p>
<p begin="913400000t" end="962200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">我有 来过…这里…</p>
<p begin="962200000t" end="975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">怎么了</p>
<p begin="975600000t" end="1003500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">你应该是第一次来这里</p>
<p begin="1008100000t" end="1039800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">但如果觉得有印象也并非不可思议</p>
<p begin="1046500000t" end="1064000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">那是什么意思</p>
<p begin="1092800000t" end="1122000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">父…父亲 请跟艾连说明</p>
<p begin="1127400000t" end="1143600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">我也是这么打算</p>
<p begin="1148200000t" end="1181200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">但想先试一件事</p>
<p begin="1188300000t" end="1230800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">这么做 他或许就会想起来了</p>
<p begin="1338800000t" end="1364300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">这是…什么…</p>
<p begin="1364700000t" end="1384700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">这不是我看到的束西</p>
<p begin="1399700000t" end="1433500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">不对 这是谁的记亿</p>
<p begin="1454000000t" end="1466500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">那只钥匙</p>
<p begin="1474800000t" end="1487700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">这是…</p>
<p begin="1498200000t" end="1509400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">难道说</p>
<p begin="1719600000t" end="1743000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">爸…爸…</p>
<p begin="1821800000t" end="1834300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">怎么样</p>
<p begin="1881500000t" end="1897300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">你想起来了吗</p>
<p begin="1897700000t" end="1919000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">想起你父亲的罪孽</p>
<p begin="2835100000t" end="2885100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">罪孽</p>
<p begin="2914200000t" end="2931700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">真厉害呢 希丝特莉亚</p>
<p begin="2932100000t" end="2956300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">你竟然已经看得懂这么多了</p>
<p begin="2959600000t" end="2988800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">因为有姐姐教我呀</p>
<p begin="2993400000t" end="3019700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">不可以哟 这样挂着鼻涕</p>
<p begin="3022200000t" end="3053900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">希丝特莉亚得更有女孩的样子才行呢</p>
<p begin="3057600000t" end="3072700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">来 用力</p>
<p begin="3110600000t" end="3132300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">很好 做得好哟</p>
<p begin="3171100000t" end="3193600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">女孩的样子是什么</p>
<p begin="3196900000t" end="3238700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">这个嘛 像女孩的样子</p>
<p begin="3239100000t" end="3265800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">应该就是像这个女孩这样吧</p>
<p begin="3269500000t" end="3284500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">克里斯塔</p>
<p begin="3284900000t" end="3293700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">没错</p>
<p begin="3294100000t" end="3317900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">希丝特莉亚也喜欢克里斯塔吧</p>
<p begin="3330400000t" end="3373400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">因为克里斯塔是很为人着想的温柔女孩呢</p>
<p begin="3376300000t" end="3400500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">希丝特莉亚也变得像她一样吧</p>
<p begin="3405900000t" end="3440500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">这世上有太多艰辛痛苦的事情了</p>
<p begin="3444300000t" end="3466800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">所以你得变成受人喜爱的人</p>
<p begin="3467200000t" end="3495200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">跟大家互相帮助一起活下去</p>
<p begin="3515600000t" end="3547700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">那我想要变成像姐姐一样</p>
<p begin="3557300000t" end="3598200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">等我长大能变成像姐姐一样的人吗</p>
<p begin="3624900000t" end="3636600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">没关系啦</p>
<p begin="3636600000t" end="3651200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">没关系 没关系的</p>
<p begin="3651600000t" end="3668700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">你只要保持这样就好了</p>
<p begin="3744200000t" end="3760400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">对不起哟 希丝特莉亚</p>
<p begin="3760800000t" end="3779200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">时间已经到了</p>
<p begin="3782100000t" end="3807600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">今天也忘记我的事情吧</p>
<p begin="3807600000t" end="3825100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">直到我们下次再见面的时候</p>
<p begin="3961500000t" end="4005700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">咦？那个女生 是谁啊</p>
<p begin="4118300000t" end="4141600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">怎么了 希丝特莉亚</p>
<p begin="4146200000t" end="4200000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">为什么 为什么我至今都忘记了呢</p>
<p begin="4212100000t" end="4233000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">我不是一个人</p>
<p begin="4237200000t" end="4268900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">我还有那个姐姐</p>
<p begin="4285100000t" end="4326800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">给我书 教我阅读写字</p>
<p begin="4326800000t" end="4345200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">对我很温柔</p>
<p begin="4348500000t" end="4372300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">我怎么会忘了她呢</p>
<p begin="4385200000t" end="4409400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">原来你跟芙莉妲曾经见过吗</p>
<p begin="4415300000t" end="4428600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">芙莉妲</p>
<p begin="4432800000t" end="4469900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">如果你说的人是有一头黑长发的年轻女性</p>
<p begin="4470300000t" end="4500800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">那她应该就是芙莉妲·雷斯</p>
<p begin="4500800000t" end="4526200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">是你同父异母的姐姐</p>
<p begin="4535400000t" end="4555000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">芙莉妲一直很在意你的事</p>
<p begin="4555400000t" end="4580000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">似乎时不时就会去照顾你</p>
<p begin="4585000000t" end="4637100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">消除了你的记忆应该是为了保护你吧</p>
<p begin="4645900000t" end="4665500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">消除记忆</p>
<p begin="4675100000t" end="4729700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">而且那也随着在这碰触他而被你想起</p>
<p begin="4754300000t" end="4777300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">父亲</p>
<p begin="4777700000t" end="4805200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">芙莉妲现在人在哪</p>
<p begin="4808600000t" end="4827300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">我想见她亲口跟她道谢</p>
<p begin="4849400000t" end="4875300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">要是没有姐姐的话我一定…</p>
<p begin="4879000000t" end="4909900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">我得为了那时候的事情跟她道谢才行</p>
<p begin="4937400000t" end="4965800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">芙莉妲已经不在这个世上了</p>
<p begin="4996700000t" end="5023400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">我曾经有五个孩子</p>
<p begin="5044200000t" end="5088400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">但包含妻子以及芙莉妲在内的孩子</p>
<p begin="5088800000t" end="5101800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">全都在五年前 在这里</p>
<p begin="5101800000t" end="5145590000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">被他的父亲古利夏·叶卡杀害了</p>
<p begin="5227700000t" end="5261500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">古利夏是拥有巨人之力的人</p>
<p begin="5264900000t" end="5294900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">虽然不知道他的真实身份究竟为何</p>
<p begin="5313700000t" end="5351600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">但他的目的是夺取雷斯家拥有的“力量”</p>
<p begin="5363300000t" end="5392100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">而古利夏追求的“力量”就是…</p>
<p begin="5406700000t" end="5448800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">寄宿在芙莉妲体内的巨人之力</p>
<p begin="5478800000t" end="5520500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">芙莉妲的巨人是站在所有巨人顶点的存在</p>
<p begin="5523000000t" end="5553100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">换句话说就是拥有无敌力量的巨人</p>
<p begin="5563900000t" end="5620600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">但她还不具备足够的经验驾驭这能力</p>
<p begin="5631900000t" end="5664000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">芙莉妲就这样无法发挥力量真正的价值</p>
<p begin="5664400000t" end="5708200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">被古利夏吞噬 夺走了力量</p>
<p begin="5730300000t" end="5772400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">然后他袭击了我们一家人</p>
<p begin="5776200000t" end="5804100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">为了要断绝我们雷斯家的血脉</p>
<p begin="5822900000t" end="5867500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">一掌拍烂14岁的迪尔克和12岁的阿贝尔</p>
<p begin="5867500000t" end="5905500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">用脚踩死了抱着10岁的弗洛莉安的妻子</p>
<p begin="5905500000t" end="5945100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">最后用手捏死了长子乌克林</p>
<p begin="5945500000t" end="5987700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">奇迹般地生还的只有我一个人</p>
<p begin="6049000000t" end="6063600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">怎么这样…</p>
<p begin="6081500000t" end="6101100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">为什么姐姐会…</p>
<p begin="6118200000t" end="6144100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">为什么做得出这么可怕的事</p>
<p begin="6284600000t" end="6317200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">你们还有闲情逸致聊天</p>
<p begin="6324200000t" end="6351800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">外面现在可闹翻天了耶</p>
<p begin="6362200000t" end="6390600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">是肯尼吗…发生什么事了</p>
<p begin="6394700000t" end="6441900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">调查军团发起政变 全军团都反叛啦</p>
<p begin="6441900000t" end="6469400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">国王大人是假货的事情被发现</p>
<p begin="6469400000t" end="6495200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">大人物们也全都被逮捕了</p>
<p begin="6495200000t" end="6520300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">状况可精彩了</p>
<p begin="6536100000t" end="6561600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">这里被察觉也是迟早的事</p>
<p begin="6561600000t" end="6582800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">麻烦你们动作决点吧</p>
<p begin="6586200000t" end="6602900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">我知道了</p>
<p begin="6605800000t" end="6646600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">你们对人压制部队就固守入口吧</p>
<p begin="6657100000t" end="6705500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">我应该说过举行仪式需要你们离开吧</p>
<p begin="6705500000t" end="6734200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">怎么了 国王大人 生气了</p>
<p begin="6754300000t" end="6792200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">是我不好啦 毕竟我天生爱操心呢</p>
<p begin="6798900000t" end="6842300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">肯尼 我很信任你的 去吧</p>
<p begin="6842700000t" end="6864800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">我也是 国王大人</p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">现在可以公开情报</p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133"></p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134"></p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135"></p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136"></p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137"></p>
<p begin="6925000000t" end="6975100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138"></p>
<p begin="6991600000t" end="7049100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">接下来所有进食都得请您用下面摄入</p>
<p begin="7049600000t" end="7101300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">宽着的服饰也仅有滕盖以下的鞋袜</p>
<p begin="7101300000t" end="7158000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">并以这个形象每周在民众面前露面一次</p>
<p begin="7172200000t" end="7190100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">真美呀</p>
<p begin="7193900000t" end="7233100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">世上恐伯不存在能超越您的艺术品吧</p>
<p begin="7233500000t" end="7268900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">不枉费我花了几十年构思呢</p>
<p begin="7268900000t" end="7320700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">在将此形象展现在被各位大人草菅人命的民众面前时</p>
<p begin="7320700000t" end="7357400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">这个作品才算真正完成</p>
<p begin="7357400000t" end="7392000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">萨克雷 你给走着瞧</p>
<p begin="7394500000t" end="7427400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">你的血是奴隶之血</p>
<p begin="7430400000t" end="7466600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">与我们贵族的高贵血统是不同的</p>
<p begin="7466600000t" end="7512900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">你立刻就会失去记忆 连上厕所的方法都…</p>
<p begin="7532500000t" end="7560900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">又是同一套威胁啊</p>
<p begin="7560900000t" end="7583400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">就没有点新说法吗</p>
<p begin="7604700000t" end="7622600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">糟糕了呢 艾尔文</p>
<p begin="7629300000t" end="7661000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">王政干部所有人都说了一样的话</p>
<p begin="7661400000t" end="7688100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">完全符合你跟你父亲的假设呢</p>
<p begin="7699000000t" end="7744800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">这意味着雷斯家能够随心所欲地窜改人类的记忆</p>
<p begin="7744800000t" end="7776500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">而且那口气听起来 似乎包含他们在内</p>
<p begin="7776500000t" end="7808600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">有一部分家族血统是不会受到影响的</p>
<p begin="7817400000t" end="7832800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">竟然有这种事</p>
<p begin="7837400000t" end="7870800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">也就是说雷斯只要拿到艾连拥有的“座标”之力</p>
<p begin="7870800000t" end="7906200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">就能完全抹灭曾有民众反叛的事实</p>
<p begin="7911700000t" end="7958800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">证据就是所有人仗着这点恬不知耻地把事情全抖出来了</p>
<p begin="7958800000t" end="7986300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">毕竟嘴硬也只是讨打而已</p>
<p begin="7988000000t" end="8001800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">原来如此…</p>
<p begin="8001800000t" end="8046800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">是认定即便如此重要的情报我们也肯定会忘记</p>
<p begin="8053100000t" end="8089300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">应该也是觉得与其落入萨克雷手里</p>
<p begin="8089300000t" end="8135600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">还不如继续接受我们的拷问吧</p>
<p begin="8143600000t" end="8163200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">真令人搞不懂呢</p>
<p begin="8163200000t" end="8203200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">没想到这竟是他的终生之愿…</p>
<p begin="8203200000t" end="8232000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">司令…您早就知道了</p>
<p begin="8232000000t" end="8282900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">啊 说溜嘴了…没错</p>
<p begin="8292900000t" end="8325000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">我早就发现达里斯·萨克雷的野心了</p>
<p begin="8333300000t" end="8363800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">我跟你不同 不喜欢赌博</p>
<p begin="8368800000t" end="8391700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">还有一点跟你们不一样的是</p>
<p begin="8391700000t" end="8429700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">比起自己我更在乎能有多少人类存活下来</p>
<p begin="8443900000t" end="8498100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">之所以答应你的提案是因为觉得这对人类来说是最好的选择</p>
<p begin="8500200000t" end="8533500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">如果判断还是应该跟随王政府</p>
<p begin="8534400000t" end="8566500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">也做好必须与萨克雷相争的觉悟</p>
<p begin="8581100000t" end="8634500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">就连我们刚政变成功的同伴之间都是这副德行了</p>
<p begin="8637400000t" end="8677400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">记得有人说过人总有一天会停止彼此斗争</p>
<p begin="8677800000t" end="8694500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">那一天要才会到来呢</p>
<p begin="8712500000t" end="8749200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">团长所有人准备完毕</p>
<p begin="8754600000t" end="8767900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">随时可以出发</p>
<p begin="8793400000t" end="8818000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">等到人类数量灭绝到一人以下之时</p>
<p begin="8818400000t" end="8845500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">就不可能再出现人类之间的斗争了</p>
<p begin="8869300000t" end="8903100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">我才不想听你这种歪理呢</p>
<p begin="8908500000t" end="8925600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">全员整队</p>
<p begin="8928900000t" end="8975600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">即刻执行艾连及希丝特莉亚的夺回计划</p>
<p begin="8976500000t" end="9016900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">立刻前往目的地雷斯领地礼拜堂</p>
<p begin="9043600000t" end="9058600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">知道了吗</p>
<p begin="9059100000t" end="9077800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">开膛手肯尼</p>
<p begin="9077800000t" end="9105400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">只要他在场 他就是最大威胁</p>
<p begin="9107900000t" end="9143300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">要说威胁的严重程度 就想成敌方里有我</p>
<p begin="9143300000t" end="9178300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">不 只要有那种武器就比我还棘手</p>
<p begin="9178300000t" end="9208000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">那靠我们就不可能了呀</p>
<p begin="9208000000t" end="9231700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">如果等跟军团汇合…</p>
<p begin="9231700000t" end="9245100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">绝对不行</p>
<p begin="9245500000t" end="9260100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">没错绝对不行</p>
<p begin="9260500000t" end="9291400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">因为等到早上说不定艾连就被吃掉了呢</p>
<p begin="9292200000t" end="9350600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">但从兵长的描述听来似乎也不是没有弱点</p>
<p begin="9350600000t" end="9362300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">真的吗 阿尔敏</p>
<p begin="9370200000t" end="9405700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">就算有进行训练 如果不习惯实战的话就更…</p>
<p begin="9405700000t" end="9451100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">可是明明一起住过 开膛手肯尼的情报却只有这一点点</p>
<p begin="9452000000t" end="9470300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">到底是怎么回事啊 里维</p>
<p begin="9470700000t" end="9510300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">抱歉 我也是昨天才知道他的全名</p>
<p begin="9513700000t" end="9538700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">似乎是肯尼·阿卡曼</p>
<p begin="9542500000t" end="9562500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">说不定是你亲戚呢</p>
<p begin="9595000000t" end="9644200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">据父母生前所说 父姓“阿卡曼”家族</p>
<p begin="9644200000t" end="9673000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">在城市里似乎受到了迫害</p>
<p begin="9685500000t" end="9711800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">身为东洋人的母亲的家族</p>
<p begin="9711800000t" end="9744300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">只因人种不同就在城镇中无立足之地</p>
<p begin="9744300000t" end="9806100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">两人都被追逼到墙壁边缘山中生活 相遇后结成了夫妻</p>
<p begin="9812700000t" end="9846900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">我不知道为什么阿卡曼家族会被迫害</p>
<p begin="9853600000t" end="9902400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">从父亲身上也看不出来像母亲那样明显的人种差异</p>
<p begin="9920300000t" end="9979600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">你有过感觉体内力量突然觉醒的经验吗</p>
<p begin="10052600000t" end="10063000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">有的</p>
<p begin="10131000000t" end="10166800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">肯尼·阿卡曼似乎也有一样的经验</p>
<p begin="10172700000t" end="10194400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">在某个时刻 每个瞬间</p>
<p begin="10194400000t" end="10227700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">突然间从体内各处涌出莫名的力量</p>
<p begin="10227700000t" end="10254800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">而身体也很自然地知道该怎么做</p>
<p begin="10262800000t" end="10293190000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">我也经历过那样的瞬闲</p>
<p begin="10434600000t" end="10456300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">都说出来吧 老头子</p>
<p begin="10468000000t" end="10493400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">你要死了吧</p>
<p begin="10519700000t" end="10572200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">肯尼 你又杀了宪兵吗</p>
<p begin="10590200000t" end="10616000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">如果你是说那些在附近打探的家伙</p>
<p begin="10616900000t" end="10643600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">我把他们都变成田里的肥料了</p>
<p begin="10669400000t" end="10719900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">分家似乎移住到南边希干希纳区的角落了</p>
<p begin="10727400000t" end="10765800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">不过在那似乎也有人妨碍生意</p>
<p begin="10766200000t" end="10793700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">好像依旧很贫困呢</p>
<p begin="10800400000t" end="10817100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">到底怎么回事</p>
<p begin="10822100000t" end="10862500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">听说过去阿卡曼家祖是国王亲信的武家</p>
<p begin="10863400000t" end="10893800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">现在却落到将要血脉断绝的窘境</p>
<p begin="10898000000t" end="10930100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">到底做了什么才被王政府恨成这样</p>
<p begin="10955500000t" end="10990200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">快说啦 你不是最疼孙子了吗</p>
<p begin="11044400000t" end="11074000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">以前那个可爱的孙子</p>
<p begin="11074800000t" end="11121100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">现在成了震惊全城的“开膛手肯尼”吗</p>
<p begin="11129500000t" end="11169100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">阿卡曼家族并非被王政府增限</p>
<p begin="11169100000t" end="11194100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">而是被畏惧着</p>
<p begin="11197000000t" end="11245800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">因为王无法操纵阿卡曼家族啊</p>
<p begin="11251300000t" end="11266700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">操纵</p>
<p begin="11272500000t" end="11303400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">我也不是知道所有真相</p>
<p begin="11303400000t" end="11371400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">但过去我们一族的确曾是隶属王政的利刃</p>
<p begin="11371400000t" end="11402200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">是王政中枢的其中一支</p>
<p begin="11406000000t" end="11466500000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">王则代代继承巨人之力保有力量</p>
<p begin="11479800000t" end="11504800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">巨人之力 你说什么</p>
<p begin="11504800000t" end="11529400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">那份力量十分强大</p>
<p begin="11529900000t" end="11590800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">能窜改所有人类的记忆令人忘却过去</p>
<p begin="11590800000t" end="11619100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">除了少数血脉以外</p>
<p begin="11623300000t" end="11669200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">而在那之中与王政为敌的家族有两个</p>
<p begin="11675400000t" end="11722100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">那就是东洋一族和阿卡曼家族</p>
<p begin="11728400000t" end="11749300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">所以才被迫害吗…</p>
<p begin="11755500000t" end="11776800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">真是残酷</p>
<p begin="11818500000t" end="11850200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">这对将死之人司能说不上安慰</p>
<p begin="11852700000t" end="11874400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">不过我终于找到妹妹了</p>
<p begin="11882700000t" end="11916900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">库契尔曾在地下街道的娼馆工作</p>
<p begin="11917300000t" end="11937800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">怀上了客人的孩子…</p>
<p begin="11945300000t" end="11970700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">说什么都不听硬要生下来</p>
<p begin="11983700000t" end="11993700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">真是的</p>
<p begin="11999500000t" end="12031200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">被生在这种满是垃圾的世界</p>
<p begin="12031200000t" end="12061600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">哪能做什么美梦呢</p>
<p begin="12106700000t" end="12117100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">有了</p>
<p begin="12122100000t" end="12136300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">是暗门</p>
<p begin="12140100000t" end="12161700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">艾连和敌人应该都在里面吧</p>
<p begin="12164700000t" end="12195100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">要是里面的地形和我猜测的一样就好了</p>
<p begin="12195500000t" end="12237700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">希望特地绕道准备的礼物派得上用场呢</p>
<p begin="12268900000t" end="12291900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">敌人至少有七个人以上</p>
<p begin="12294000000t" end="12323600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">这里面当然也包含里维在内</p>
<p begin="12330200000t" end="12345700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">如你们所知</p>
<p begin="12346100000t" end="12373600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">里维在完全被奇袭的状态下</p>
<p begin="12373600000t" end="12402000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">杀了我们12个同伴</p>
<p begin="12410700000t" end="12468700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">而我们中央宪兵的本部和王政府也都已被镇压了呢</p>
<p begin="12475000000t" end="12489600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">状况十分严峻</p>
<p begin="12498700000t" end="12545900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">在这狭窄的世界里 投降后等着我们的</p>
<p begin="12545900000t" end="12566300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">只有比死还悲惨的命运吧</p>
<p begin="12586800000t" end="12636000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">但只要还活在这城墙里 就毫无分别吧</p>
<p begin="12651400000t" end="12668900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">眼前有不可能击败的敌人</p>
<p begin="12668900000t" end="12710200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">不知道什么时候会踏破城墙来毁灭我们</p>
<p begin="12714400000t" end="12736900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">我们之所以会选择当宪兵</p>
<p begin="12736900000t" end="12772800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">志愿进入中央宪兵 跟随肯尼</p>
<p begin="12772800000t" end="12801100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">都是为了在没有意义的世界和没有意义的人生之中</p>
<p begin="12801100000t" end="12817800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">找到属于我们的意义</p>
<p begin="12825300000t" end="12848700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">那么就试着相信到最后吧</p>
<p begin="12853700000t" end="12900400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">相信肯尼颠覆这世界的梦想</p>
<p begin="12934600000t" end="12960000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">好 准备完毕</p>
<p begin="12960000000t" end="12971700000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">是吗…</p>
<p begin="12978800000t" end="13021800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">那么你们 都有弄脏双手的觉悟了吗</p>
<p begin="13100200000t" end="13116900000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">看样子没问题了呢</p>
<p begin="13330200000t" end="13430300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">大地と大空は 何故別れたのだろう</p>
<p begin="13434100000t" end="13538400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">世界は残酷で されど美しい</p>
<p begin="13544400000t" end="13595200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">石を投げる者と 投げられる者には</p>
<p begin="13596200000t" end="13644800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">容易に越えられぬ 柵がある</p>
<p begin="13649800000t" end="13699000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">立ち位置が替われば 正義は牙を剥く</p>
<p begin="13702200000t" end="13755600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">檻の中で吼えているのは 果たしてどちらか</p>
<p begin="13758900000t" end="13825400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">心臓を捧げた 戻せない黄昏に</p>
<p begin="13827600000t" end="13900300000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">進み続けた夜の果て 楽園は何処にある？</p>
<p begin="13912200000t" end="13951400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">Requiem Requiem</p>
<p begin="13954200000t" end="13986000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">この夜に散った名も無き花よ</p>
<p begin="13987100000t" end="14069200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">どうか安らかに暁に眠れ</p>
<p begin="14208800000t" end="14232100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">保护他的梦想</p>
<p begin="14232100000t" end="14255100000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">将他拯救出来</p>
<p begin="14255500000t" end="14283400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">继承他的记忆</p>
<p begin="14288500000t" end="14325600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">各自的信念驱使众人舍身战斗</p>
<p begin="14334800000t" end="14350400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">次回「願い」</p>
<p begin="14334800000t" end="14350400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">下一回“愿望”</p>
